      "name": "Hemolysis index validation at 3 L/min, 2400 RPM",
      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at 3 L/min flow, 2400 RPM. Simulation over-predicts NIH by 12% within Monte Carlo uncertainty bounds."
    },
